<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">no, I don&apos;t believe so. I don&apos;t think it needs a second one, all the loose ends got tied up.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">no, I don't believe so. I don't think it needs a second one, all the loose ends got tied up.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
