<span id="freeTextContainer4372728061065700903">Remember how I was just saying I wanted a YA thriller that would actually, you know, thrill me? Here it is. <br/><br/>Those who liked certain elements of <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/16045088.Charm___Strange' title='Charm &amp; Strange by Stephanie Kuehn' rel='nofollow noopener'>Charm &amp; Strange</a> and <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/16065521.Wild_Awake' title='Wild Awake by Hilary T. Smith' rel='nofollow noopener'>Wild Awake</a> might like this, and certainly you&apos;ll like it if you enjoy books like <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/16074758.Dangerous_Girls' title='Dangerous Girls by Abigail Haas' rel='nofollow noopener'>Dangerous Girls</a>. Not a perfect book, but a really, really good one, so I&apos;m bumping it up in star ratings in support. I had never heard of Nick Lake until now, but I&apos;m definitely reading his other books! Review to come. </span>
  <span id="freeText4372728061065700903" style="display:none">Remember how I was just saying I wanted a YA thriller that would actually, you know, thrill me? Here it is. <br /><br />Those who liked certain elements of <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/16045088.Charm___Strange" title="Charm &amp; Strange by Stephanie Kuehn" rel="nofollow noopener">Charm &amp; Strange</a> and <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/16065521.Wild_Awake" title="Wild Awake by Hilary T. Smith" rel="nofollow noopener">Wild Awake</a> might like this, and certainly you'll like it if you enjoy books like <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/16074758.Dangerous_Girls" title="Dangerous Girls by Abigail Haas" rel="nofollow noopener">Dangerous Girls</a>. Not a perfect book, but a really, really good one, so I'm bumping it up in star ratings in support. I had never heard of Nick Lake until now, but I'm definitely reading his other books! Review to come. </span>
