<li class='cover' id='bookCover_21469108'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/21469108-the-ghosts-of-heaven"><img alt="The Ghosts of Heaven" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1409674391l/21469108._SX98_.jpg" />
